was founded as a consortium of three companies, [[Hydro-Québec]],[[SNC-Lavalin]], and [[Bechtel Corporation|Bechtel]], to build a series of [[hydroelectric dam]]s in northern [[Quebec]] during the 1970s and early 1980s.  Upon completion, the dams all came under the control of Hydro-Québec.
